{"tid":2468983,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[月供股票] 2021年Q2 問定唔問 睇完#1先好問 1","createTime":"2021-03-31T01:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-08T02:18:10.000Z","uid":99885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca8d3fd51e32f8a26137e187d86c66212b593ce","tid":2468983,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T01:43:09.000Z","msg":"推埋舊post先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">睇完#1先好問手續費</span></span><br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n榮譽會員:間諜巴打(教大家月供2800), 朱千雪讓我哭巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n月供po狗鐵主席: i-vtec <strong>（尚欠每人50加1股2388）</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span class=\"xx-large\">新手知識：</span></ins></strong><br />\n問：咩叫月供股票？<br />\n答：每月用你指定既金額，購買你指定既股票。<br />\n例：你set左月供$2000盈富、$2000騰訊、$2000匯豐，假設你用一通黎做月供，會係每月既第五個交易日買入。假設盈富個日係$20一股，你會買到100股，騰訊係$201一股，你會買到9股，即$1809，銀行只會扣你$1809。<br />\n<br />\n問：月供股票有咩好？<br />\n答：<br />\n1）低入場費：如果你睇好騰訊，但佢一手要大約兩萬蚊，但你冇咁多錢，月供就幫到你。你可以每月$5000咁供。<br />\n2）平均成本：假設騰訊三個月既價係：$170、$180、$190，你同樣都係月供$5000，係第一個月你會買到29股，第二個月買到27股，第三個月買到26股，變相平個陣買多啲，貴個陣買小啲。個平均買入價會係$179.63。<br />\n3）減低心理因素：由於每月都係指定個日入貨，我地唔需要睇價入，平時好多時會見佢貴，冇入到，點知就升到咩咁。<br />\n<br />\n問：啲碎股點算好？有冇息收？<br />\n答：碎股係可以放同埋係有息收的，唔需要草夠一手先有。<br />\n<br />\n問：用邊間？收費如何？<br />\n答：主要都係推介呢三間：匯豐、一通同致富。<br />\n<br />\n匯豐：月供買入無任何費用。存倉每月$25，收息費照正常價，即股息0.5%，最低消費$30；紅股每手$5，最低消費$30。無分月供倉或正股倉，無雙重存倉收費。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. Premier免存倉，耐唔耐亦有特選客戶免一年存倉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2EWmnkR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EWmnkR&d=T8vHa4Omq%2F1xxkbvjwgdjmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=76b47537\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2EWmnkR</a><br />\n <br />\n一通：所有交易都係$5，收息每次$5。如果你月供3隻，每月就係$15。收息費$5+股息0.12%香港交易所費用，紅股每次$5。無存倉費，無分月供倉或正股倉。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.i-access.com.hk/fee_c.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.i-access.com.hk%2Ffee_c.html&d=T8vHa4Omq%2F1xxkbvjwgdjmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=6c15b38a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.i-access.com.hk/fee_c.html</a><br />\n<br />\n致富：每隻股票每次供款頭$10000免佣；即係你供100隻、每隻$2000都係免佣；其後收0.0675%(無最低收費)，另收印花稅、交易徵費、聯交所交易費及結算所收費。以供1000蚊爲例，印花稅、交易徵費、聯交所交易費及結算所收費合共$6.08<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問：有咩記數app?<br />\n答：<br />\n1. Ticker。非常清晰咁記錄你既交易同會自動幫你計你個平均買入價。<br />\n或者自己整Google Sheet<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. Stocker<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2106125/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2106125/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n問：比較受歡迎既月供選擇？<br />\n答：盈富基金、煤氣、匯豐、領展、港鐵、中銀香港、中電、建行、騰訊、港交所。<br />\n<br />\n問：＿＿幾號截數唔畀改、扣數、買入？<br />\n答：<br />\n匯豐：扣數日為每月八號，如當日為禮拜六/日或公假，則提前一工作日扣數；截數日為扣數日前五個工作日；買入日為扣數日後第三個工作日，入倉日為入貨日後第二個工作日。入倉日後第二個工作日寄statement。<br />\n<br />\n一通：五號十點前入數，五號會買入，如紅日就下一個交易日，statement會係第二日就出。<br />\n<br />\n致富：每月有兩次供款日，供款日為每月第五個及第十五個交易日，可以自己選月頭或月尾供或兩日都供，截數及扣數時間為供款日上午8:30，此時間前可以改金額或暫停（即係可以睇住黎食）。通常大約10-12時買入股票，即日下午左右會知派彩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n問：mark數入唔入手續費好？<br />\n答：自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問：點解仲未扣數/入數？<br />\n答：睇上面日子，過左都未有打去問CS<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先，其他留待其他巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>此post純屬討論，並不為任何投資決策負責。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n   <br />\n月供po港鐵主席ok-i笑話幾則:<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/182901_4b5c03449524e0ccb4a8f5421f03dc9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F182901_4b5c03449524e0ccb4a8f5421f03dc9a.png&h=cf5a9acd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/101801_91b3406b0bf44beffc94299720f994d4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F101801_91b3406b0bf44beffc94299720f994d4.png&h=b3b75a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWNy5hRApVRWDeRBUR9bKtdiG1N1Cr6MD8EF8mQZ1q1Jd?filename=1XehZqd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XehZqd.png&h=0adafe2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQGyR9Yk2aCr2refW3JUDqDSNuQBo1tt6s2ERvGh3tPPm?filename=Kv4g2kR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKv4g2kR.jpg&h=8addec9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTbS8JBDMdV3AwmWZTh4qocjGhBht9r5Axu2Z4sn7sSjb?filename=z11N2Wz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz11N2Wz.png&h=86835ad2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23d1af2784d34cae391a4f364e85ac3f667181fb","tid":2468983,"uid":94836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T02:00:07.000Z","msg":"全線舊經濟Mola mola"},{"pid":"e0f88a9d83508e2751886d1cd6bfd7278ac471fb","tid":2468983,"uid":29